768
01:14:26,320 --> 01:14:29,915
lmaš ženu u
Arkansasu? -Nemam.

769
01:14:30,320 --> 01:14:34,199
Hoceš plesati?
-Svakako.

770
01:15:39,160 --> 01:15:41,879
Bolnicarkin ured.
-Zdravstvena postaja.

771
01:15:42,560 --> 01:15:46,189
