799
01:18:50,920 --> 01:18:52,911
Kad sam smiren...

800
01:18:54,920 --> 01:18:57,388
Kad sam tužan...

801
01:18:59,240 --> 01:19:03,677
Sjajno! Baš
mi se svida.

802
01:19:04,400 --> 01:19:08,313
Ne bih prodao posao,
ali ovo jest snažno.

803
01:19:09,120 --> 01:19:12,874
lma još. -ldi na
kraj. Na sam kraj.

804
01:19:15,880 --> 01:19:18,030
...neko vrijeme.

805
01:19:18,640 --> 01:19:20,790
To je dobro!

806
01:19:21,600 --> 01:19:24,797
Neko vrijeme. -Sjajno!
-Hoceš šmrkati? -Ne.

807
01:19:29,680 --> 01:19:33,878
Evo. -Nedostajao
si mi. -l ti meni.

808
01:19:58,680 --> 01:20:01,433
Buducnost je
NENAPlSANA!

809
01:21:52,760 --> 01:21:54,591
Nisam ja.

810
01:21:58,200 --> 01:21:59,792
Nisam.

811
01:22:04,480 --> 01:22:06,994
Što je? Gdje je
naš decko? Gdje?

812
01:22:15,040 --> 01:22:16,837
Krv?

813
01:22:19,800 --> 01:22:23,315
Svaki dan ubijaju nevine.
-Je li ovaj mrtav?

814
01:22:23,640 --> 01:22:27,872
Milijunašev ljubimac strada
i oznacen si za cijeli život.

815
01:22:30,160 --> 01:22:31,718
Pomozi.

816
01:22:34,280 --> 01:22:36,157
Skini ono.

817
01:22:36,920 --> 01:22:38,797
VJERUJ l POSTlGNl!

