821
01:22:52,120 --> 01:22:54,395
Noge su mu pokrivene?

822
01:22:58,240 --> 01:22:59,673
ldemo.

823
01:23:01,080 --> 01:23:02,911
Primi mu noge.

824
01:23:35,200 --> 01:23:37,191
Stavi ga ondje.

825
01:23:45,080 --> 01:23:46,229
Jedan...

826
01:23:47,160 --> 01:23:48,309
Dva...

827
01:23:50,680 --> 01:23:51,635
Tri.

828
01:23:54,760 --> 01:23:56,113
Ulazi.

829
01:23:57,280 --> 01:23:59,077
